OL,3,CNurses say patients are dying in
OL,4,C'corridor care crisis'
OL,6,FThe report includes testimonies from
OL,7,Fmore than 5,000 nurses in the UK, as
OL,8,FITV News' Faye Barker reports
OL,10,FThe Royal College of Nurses (RCN) has
OL,11,Fsaid there is a "corridor care crisis"
OL,12,Fin hospitals across the UK, with
OL,13,Ftestimonies from more than 5,000
OL,14,Fnurses in the UK, including 500 from
OL,15,FScotland, including harrowing stories
OL,16,Fof patients suffering and dying in
OL,17,Fhospital corridors because they aren't
OL,18,Fgetting the care they need.
