OL,6,FThe RCN said its 400-page report must
OL,7,Fbe a "wake-up call" for the country's
OL,8,Fpolitical leaders.
OL,10,FScotland's NHS has been hit with a
OL,11,F"devastating collapse in care
OL,12,Fstandards", with patients "routinely
OL,13,Fcoming to harm" and unable to access
OL,14,Fbasic services, the RCN report found.
