OL,6,FOne nurse said in the report: "This
OL,7,Fmorning staff left in tears as we had
OL,8,Fa cardiac arrest in a corridor where
OL,9,Fwe couldn't move the bed to the resus
OL,10,Farea as there were other patients on
OL,11,Fbeds blocking access. Sadly this lady
OL,12,Fdied."
