OL,6,FAnother said: "A 90-year lady with
OL,7,Fdementia was scared crying and
OL,8,Furinating in the bed after asking
OL,9,Fseveral times for help to the toilet.
OL,10,FSeeing that lady, frightened and
OL,11,Fsubjected to animal-like conditions is
OL,12,Fwhat broke me. At the end of that
OL,13,Fshift, I handed in my notice with no
OL,14,Fjob to go to."
OL,16,FThe nursing union said "demoralised"
OL,17,Fstaff across the nation's hospitals
OL,18,Fhave witnessed patients going into
OL,19,Fcardiac arrest while forced to lay in
OL,20,Fcorridors due to a lack of beds.
