OL,6,FNine in 10 of those surveyed said
OL,7,Fpatient safety is being compromised.
OL,9,FA Scottish nurse said: "Department
OL,10,Fwith capacity for 13 beds, we had 40
OL,11,Fin, with patients on chairs having
OL,12,Ftreatments administered, also sitting
OL,13,Fin the waiting room on cardiac
OL,14,Fmonitors, using privacy screens to put
OL,15,Faround patients to use the bedpan."
OL,17,FOne unnamed member of staff said they
OL,18,Fwere forced to clean an elderly
OL,19,Fincontinent patient in the charge
OL,20,Fnurse's office.
