OL,10,Fthe ward multiple times.
OL,12,F"A bed was eventually found in a
OL,13,Ftemporary area which was an office
OL,14,Fusually used for out-patients
OL,15,Fappointments, it still had the
OL,16,Fcomputer desk set up and had no window
