OL,6,FA nursing support worker said: "My
OL,7,Flast shift, I went into a full ward
OL,8,Fand 34 patients were referred to come
OL,9,Finto the ward, 10 of which were in the
OL,10,Fcorridor already waiting.
OL,12,F"One of the patients had a stroke,
OL,13,Fanother with an increased oxygen
OL,14,Frequirement and several with the flu.
OL,15,FExtremely unsafe as patients kept on
OL,16,Farriving with nowhere to move our
OL,17,Falready admitted patients to."
