OL,6,FThe RCN, the UK's largest nursing
OL,7,Funion, said staffing levels have not
OL,8,Fbeen increased to cover the rise in
OL,9,Fpatient numbers.
OL,11,FThe scale of the issue, the report
OL,12,Fstated, has prompted concerns about
OL,13,Finfection prevention and control as
OL,14,Fpatients are "crammed into tight
OL,15,Fspaces next to one another".
