OL,6,FOne nurse said: "Flu-positive patients
OL,7,Fare being transferred to wards before
OL,8,Frooms become available. Patients with
OL,9,Fflu then being cared for in ward
OL,10,Fcorridors next to other vulnerable
OL,11,Fpatients."
OL,13,FThe RCN said corridor care has become
OL,14,Fnormalised in NHS hospitals across the
OL,15,FUK, as nursing staff report elderly
OL,16,Fand vulnerable patients receiving
OL,17,F"undignified and unsafe" treatment.
