OL,6,FAlmost seven in 10 (66.81%) nurses
OL,7,Fsurveyed reported delivering care in
OL,8,Fovercrowded or unsuitable places `
OL,9,Flike corridors, offices, converted
OL,10,Fcupboards and even car parks ` on a
OL,11,Fdaily basis.
OL,13,FRCN Scotland director Colin Poolman
OL,14,Fsaid: "This report makes for
OL,15,Fdistressing reading and should be a
OL,16,Fwake-up call for the Scottish
OL,17,FGovernment.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
