OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F309A1737045267
OL,3,CNurses say patients are dying in
OL,4,C'corridor care crisis'
OL,6,F"The impact goes far beyond the doors
OL,7,Fof emergency departments, with nursing
OL,8,Fstaff across many acute settings
OL,9,Fdesperately struggling as they are
OL,10,Fforced to create space in clinical
OL,11,Fareas for additional unstaffed beds or
OL,12,Fprovide patient care in corridors and
OL,13,Fother inappropriate locations.
OL,15,F"This is completely unacceptable for
OL,16,Fpatient safety and staff wellbeing. No
OL,17,Fpatient should ever have to suffer the
OL,18,Frisk or indignity of being cared for
OL,19,Fin such a way ` yet it has been
OL,20,Fallowed to become normal practice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
