OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F309A1737045267
OL,3,CNurses say patients are dying in
OL,4,C'corridor care crisis'
OL,6,F"The Scottish Government must commit
OL,7,Fto publishing the data on exactly how
OL,8,Fmany patients are being cared for in
OL,9,Fthese circumstances. The public
OL,10,Fdeserves to know what is happening to
OL,11,Fpatient safety.
OL,13,F"They must also commit to long-term
OL,14,Faction and investment focused on
OL,15,Faddressing the nursing workforce
OL,16,Fshortages and building sustainable
OL,17,Fcapacity both within in the NHS and,
OL,18,Fmost importantly, within community and
OL,19,Fsocial care."
