OL,6,FScottish Conservative health
OL,7,Fspokesperson Dr Sandesh Gulhane MSP
OL,8,Fsaid: "This devastating report must be
OL,9,Fan urgent wake-up call for SNP
OL,10,Fministers.
OL,12,F"The scandalous failure of successive
OL,13,FSNP health secretaries has left nurses
OL,14,Fto deal with complete chaos in
OL,15,Fhospital corridors."
OL,17,FScottish Labour Health spokeswoman
OL,18,FDame Jackie Baillie said: "This
OL,19,Fharrowing report is a reminder of how
OL,20,Ffar standards have fallen on the SNP's
OL,21,Fwatch.
